               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380709-name-233" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18380709-name-233" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380709-name-233" type="surname" value="DAVIS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380709-name-233" type="given" value="PHINEAS"></interp>PHINEAS DAVIS</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Red Lion-square. The prisoner was my cook—on the 1st of June we gave her notice to leave—in consequence of suspicion, before she left, we had an offieer, and searched her boxes in the hall—we found a cambric handkerchief at that time, and a comb after<lb></lb>wards, which I believe are mine.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
